headline: Qualcomm (QCOM) Executes $2.4Bn AI Data Center Market Counteroffensive
summary: Qualcomm’s (QCOM) $2.4 billion acquisition of Alphawave highlights the company’s renewed push into the rapidly expanding AI data center market. This move follows Qualcomm’s earlier efforts in the data center CPU space, which were ultimately scaled back due to cost-cutting measures, legal challenges, and intense competition.
